# Vallejo Moon

Satirical local newspaper for Vallejo — *illuminating nothing since last Tuesday.* Live: https://vallejomoon.com

Co-founded by **Mikael Hill** (design/digital) and **Dwayne** (editorial).

## Structure

- **`index.html`** + **`css/styles.css`** — the live site (root level, no build step)
- **`content/articles/`** — future article drafts (Markdown)
- **`content/drafts/`** — WIP
- **`editorial/`** — mission, style, team
- **`brand/`** — logo and visual references
- **`docs/`** — collaboration workflow
- **`deploy.sh`** — deploy to Vercel from Cursor (`Cmd+Shift+B`)
- **`.github/workflows/deploy.yml`** — auto-deploy on push to `main`

## Do not commit

`.tools/`, `.vercel/`, `.env` — already in `.gitignore`

## Deploy

Agent sandbox cannot run Vercel. User deploys via **Tasks: Run Build Task** or `git push` (GitHub Actions).
